<ProjectPageLayout title="AI & Machine Learning Exploration">
    <h1>Exploring the Frontier of Local AI & Custom Tooling</h1>
    <p>
        With "AI" being peddled non-stop, and due to my earlier studies in machine learning I have always
        found the abstract concept of AI fascinating.
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>
        Working with AI technologies outside of pre-packaged solutions requires a deep
        understanding of system architecture, resource management, and the underlying
        mechanics of large language models. This hands-on experience provides invaluable
        insight into how these systems operate at a fundamental level.
    </p>
    <p>
        Rather than solely relying on cloud-based APIs, running models locally
        demands careful consideration of hardware constraints, optimization strategies,
        and the nuances of model quantization—skills that translate directly to
        building efficient, scalable software systems.
    </p>
